\begin_inset Formula $\bar{G}\sim\left[2\sqrt{6}\Gamma\left(\frac{3}{4}\right)/\Gamma\left(\frac{1}{4}\right)\right]\lambda^{-1/2}+\mathcal{O}\left(\lambda^{-1}\right)$
\end_inset

